                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="border px-4 py-2">Data Exfiltration / Insecure Resource Exposure</td>
                  <td class="border px-4 py-2">Improper exposure of sensitive resources (files, DB) without access control.</td>
                  <td class="border px-4 py-2">RBAC enforcement, path traversal prevention, data masking/redaction.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="border px-4 py-2">Installer Spoofing / Malicious Server Installation</td>
                  <td class="border px-4 py-2">User is tricked into installing a malicious MCP server.</td>
                  <td class="border px-4 py-2">Signed packages, clear installation instructions, official repo links.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="border px-4 py-2">Denial of Service (DoS)</td>
                  <td class="border px-4 py-2">Flooding the server with requests or resource exhaustion attacks.</td>
